/a></td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h5>3.1.6 Pronunciation</h5>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n<table class=\"table table-hover\">\r\n\t<thead>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 65%\">Description</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">Pages</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">Erreurs</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">R&eacute;f(s)</th>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</thead>\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>Using the ruby element</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>0</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>0</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><a class=\"ext\" data-extlink=\"\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG21/Techniques/html/H62.html\" target=\"_blank\">H62</a></td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h4>3.2 Pr&eacute;visible</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Make Web pages appear and operate in predictable ways.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>3.2.2 On Input</h5>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n<table class=\"table table-hover\">\r\n\t<thead>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 65%\">Description</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">Pages</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">Erreurs</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">R&eacute;f(s)</th>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</thead>\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>Fournir un bouton submit</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>0</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>0</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><a class=\"ext\" data-extlink=\"\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG21/Techniques/html/H32.html\" target=\"_blank\">H32</a></td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>4. Robuste</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Le contenu peut &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute; de mani&egrave;re fiable par une large vari&eacute;t&eacute; d&#39;agents utilisateurs, y compris les technologies</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>4.1 Compatible</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximize compatibility with current and future user agents, including assistive technologies.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>4.1.1 Analyse syntaxique</h5>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n<table class=\"table table-hover\">\r\n\t<thead>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 65%\">